Set address of local machine's ethernet port to 192.0.0.128
unlpug camera's power supply (POE or barrel jack)
make sure you've got the right version of digicap-file in local directory of tftp server
start tftp server (best: python)
plug in camera power
wait some seconds (5..10), tftp server should display handshake message
wait some more seconds (up to ~30), tftp download to camera should start
wait for download to complete
unplug (!!!) local machine's network (ethernet) connection (else update will restart after camera restart)
wait some time (minutes) until camera has completed boot process
camera shows up as 192.168.1.64
happily set up camera according to your network configuration and requirements.
